aimed reforms concerning the citizen\u2019s access to quality services, social justice, policy-level improvement, good governance and administrative reforms during his time at the office.\n\nImplementation of the provision of 10 percent free hospital beds for the poor ones and the formulation of the National Health Finance Strategy (2080-2090 BS) and the Nepal Health Sector Strategic Plan were outlined as major accomplishments of the health minister\u2019s 100 days at the office.","title":"Health Minister claims visible changes in health sector in six months","url":"http://english.khabarhub.com/2023/12/314190/","video":[]}
